"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?28/19/28986?source=see_link\">",
"      Management of persistent hyperglycemia in type 2 diabetes mellitus",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?25/2/25641?source=see_link\">",
